Method\par
Accepted values: 0, 1 or 2. If value = 0 then Quest is autocompleted (skip objectives/details).\par
ZoneOrSort\par
This field defines under what category the quest falls in the quest log.\par
If value > 0 then value is Zone IDs taken from AreaTable.dbc.\par
if value < 0 then (-value) is quest sort id: (in general profession or class quests. Also see RequiredSkillValue ) Value is ID from QuestSort.dbc. QuestSort.dbc\par
SkillOrClass\par
This field defines any specific skill or class requirements for the quest to be available for a character.\par
If value > 0 then value is a skill ID (see SkillLine.dbc)\par
If value < 0 then (-value) is class ID (see ChrClasses.dbc)\par
